&lt;p&gt;West Lancashire Integrated CMHT is an Older Adults Community Mental Health service based at Brookside, Ormskirk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity for a Band 5 Mental Health Practitioner to join our Team. The position is permanent and for 27 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a multi- disciplinary team, with close working links with other health departments, social services and voluntary agencies, 5 days a week service with operating hours from 8am to 6pm.&lt;br /&gt;Our service users can present with both functional and organic mental health difficulties which are often combined with complex social care and physical health needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;James Heath&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;James.Heath@lscft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
